AVI to Sell Denny Mushrooms to Investors Led by FirstRand’s Rand Merchant

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-07-13T07:07:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-13/avi-to-sell-denny-mushrooms-to-investors-led-by-firstrand-s-rand-merchant.html
AVI Ltd. (AVI)  said it agreed to sell its
Denny Mushrooms Ltd. unit to a group of investors that include
the private-equity business of  FirstRand Ltd. (FSR) ’s Rand Merchant
Bank.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
